{"tid":1469819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]幫手搞連儂牆就同我入黎，係時候改變一下","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:07:24.000Z","uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"297d8629a4b433e1e6285a3a1512fef39d043ddf","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"大家有冇覺得，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">連儂牆的資訊好混亂好唔集中</span></span></strong>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過期文宣</span></strong>都仲係度，所有野抄埋一碟；<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">連儂牆的效力已經大不如前</span></span></strong>。比著我係路過的人都唔會知邊張係最新資訊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家已經達到一個同撕紙狗共生的現象，不斷幫我地清舊野。但要做到有效文宣，有吸引力；<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我地係咪應該每一個連儂牆都劃分一個Zone出黎；每日update最新的Poster？</span></span></strong>就好似下圖咁：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wba1SaP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwba1SaP.jpg&h=a2bd2d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靈感來自青衣站天橋個&quot;以眼還眼&quot;，成大塊巨型紙皮放係門口定期Update；吸引到好多人睇。但我依家冇圖<br />\n<br />\n至於應唔應該再劃分其他Zone，我就覺得冇必要；但我覺得一定要有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一個Zone去每日Update，連儂牆先可以達到最大的效果，將最新資訊傳比所有人！ </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正如大家所見，歷黎最大型文宣戰已經開打；包括早前的721、805、811、以眼還眼、813機場事件以及818民陣大遊行等等。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全民文宣好緊要，唔可以再只靠民間記者會。連儂牆都要進化，</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">認同請推比全世界睇 + 分享</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n警世！仲有無人記得當年各區派傳單同放映會盛況<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431353</a>"},{"pid":"4f1f10d03ce6fb59517cee99b5549584e1f9b2e3","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"3eaa948a800bfd4e1d23bad2dfb54d319e435d9d","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bcc1bca91e28257b320e1889cf4483026aa65121","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"6a6dea760c24c28147145f79f69adb50443a71c2","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8e4410a15ec40f42b40c851dd7bceed8c6cbb5b2","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5689132956d246985489fe7a7a0359baf9459916","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5e7a14e499865986016c099a215e82be2397091a","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c39ca837cc61cb73c90af1df6406f74ee67e1f52","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cb050fc99b8d46db83db58708025af7faa10cdd4","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5a783235c05a7e0765d1fea3877175fa1fb9cf7a","tid":1469819,"uid":302215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"b62e6c79d8c6